editorialNotes.standard: No green thumb? No problem! Nurture a windowsill garden in this relaxing idle game by catching raindrops and sunshine.

If you like rhythm games, you’ve got to check out Voez. You tap, swipe and press to the beat—all while the tracks are swirling around the screen, fantastic music is blasting and colours burst in every direction. It’s as awesome as it sounds.

name: Sprunki Life Sim Cute vs Scary

ios.subtitle: Play k-pop songs on the piano!

editorialNotes.standard: This rhythm-based platfomer is the kind of game that nestles in your head and won’t let go. Bouncing to a beat, you spring across gaps, between columns and over spikes—struggling to finish each wildly difficult stage. Slick controls make the game easy to pick up and play, but mastering its many challenges won’t come easily.
Spotting the minute differences in every beautiful scene of this relaxing 3D puzzler takes a keen eye.
